problem_data.title: Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters
problem_data.description: Given a string s, find the length of the longest substring without duplicate characters.

examples.explanation: The answer is "abc", with the length of 3. Note that "bca" and "cab" are also correct answers.
The answer is "b", with the length of 1.
